00:00:00.089 --> 00:00:16.230
Through the latter half of 
the 19th century, Mark Twain was on a mission

00:00:16.230 --> 00:00:18.680
to attack pretense with satire.

00:00:18.680 --> 00:00:23.550
One of his most hilarious, if completely scandalous
and by many standards inappropriate, works

00:00:23.550 --> 00:00:29.970
