in 1879 about masturbation titled, “Some

00:00:29.970 --> 00:00:31.980
Thoughts on the Science of Onanism.”

00:00:31.980 --> 00:00:36.680
During the 19th century, medical practice
had been increasingly incorporating scientific

00:00:36.680 --> 00:00:41.410
thoughts and developments, including how disease
spread and the rise of anesthesia.

00:00:41.410 --> 00:00:46.101
As such, simply calling something a “science”
at that time gave it a certain cachet, so

00:00:46.101 --> 00:00:50.860
the irony of juxtaposing this honorific with
the topic of self-abuse (as masturbation used

00:00:50.860 --> 00:00:54.079
