the audience.

00:00:54.079 --> 00:00:59.079
Nor would any part of Twain’s talk go unappreciated,
as The Stomach Club was a group of writers

00:00:59.079 --> 00:01:03.020
and artists who loved to get together over
a delicious meal, and a few too many drinks,

00:01:03.020 --> 00:01:05.189
and enjoy a bawdy tale.

00:01:05.189 --> 00:01:10.109
That evening, Twain’s topic would not disappoint,
